Dialogue: 0,00:21:14.44,00:21:16.70,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}凌晨四点
Dialogue: 0,00:21:17.47,00:21:19.71,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}为何还没入睡
Dialogue: 0,00:21:19.74,00:21:22.34,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}在这糟糕的日子 听着"Bye Bye Black Birds"
Dialogue: 0,00:21:22.44,00:21:26.16,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}自言自语也无法消除不安
Dialogue: 0,00:21:26.96,00:21:28.79,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}最近几个小时
Dialogue: 0,00:21:28.95,00:21:32.10,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我总是不断哭泣  宝贝
Dialogue: 0,00:21:33.55,00:21:36.78,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}希望你在这里
Dialogue: 0,00:21:38.94,00:21:43.47,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}看你给我的那些信
Dialogue: 0,00:21:43.57,00:21:49.38,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}每读一遍  痛苦都会消失
Dialogue: 0,00:21:49.70,00:21:52.61,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你不会孤单
Dialogue: 0,00:21:52.83,00:21:55.39,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我们四人在一起
Dialogue: 0,00:21:55.60,00:22:01.63,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}就算离别也不能拆散我们  相信着你
Dialogue: 0,00:22:01.90,00:22:07.78,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}一直在我身边
Dialogue: 0,00:22:07.97,00:22:12.58,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}靠近我  为你送上一颗四叶草
Dialogue: 0,00:22:12.81,00:22:14.40,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}祝你好运
Dialogue: 0,00:22:14.40,00:22:17.16,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你知道你不会孤单
Dialogue: 0,00:22:17.42,00:22:20.14,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我们四人在一起
Dialogue: 0,00:22:20.27,00:22:26.30,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}就算离别也不能拆散我们  你就在我心中
Dialogue: 0,00:22:26.54,00:22:32.35,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}因为我一直在你身边
Dialogue: 0,00:22:32.55,00:22:37.20,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}靠近我  为你送上一颗四叶草
Dialogue: 0,00:22:37.42,00:22:39.52,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}祝你好运
Dialogue: 0,00:02:01.44,00:02:06.78,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}指引着我  前往远方
Dialogue: 0,00:02:06.98,00:02:15.17,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}一路披荆斩棘  杀出血路
Dialogue: 0,00:02:17.41,00:02:20.35,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Yo guess who’s back Everybody get down
Dialogue: 0,00:02:20.42,00:02:23.15,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}guess who’s back hey step up step up!
Dialogue: 0,00:02:33.90,00:02:38.24,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}被命运捉弄  I’m falling down
Dialogue: 0,00:02:38.51,00:02:43.64,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}与你同奏的和声  再也不会响起
Dialogue: 0,00:02:43.71,00:02:48.84,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你强烈的香气还在心头萦绕
Dialogue: 0,00:02:49.62,00:02:51.97,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我不愿再继续等待
Dialogue: 0,00:02:53.44,00:02:55.19,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Hey guess who’s back
Dialogue: 0,00:02:55.52,00:02:58.81,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}带着愿望
Dialogue: 0,00:02:58.81,00:03:00.56,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)} guess who’s back
